Span.Text: A single mobile dashboard allows Officers to have access to relevant information in the community.
Intelligence reports, crime reports and incidents are all available via their mobile phone.

Use mobile and portable devices to gather and report data and intelligence from the scene of an incident or investigation, including POLE (people, objects, locations, and events) and SAR (suspicious activity reporting).  With security-enhanced mobile connections to the agency network or command centre, the digital evidence or intelligence can be quickly uploaded, reviewed, and distributed to other agencies, jurisdictions, or justice officials.
